REHEARING DOCKET

90-1578. Sturm v. Sturm.

Ashtabula County, No. 89-A-1451. Reported at 61 Ohio St.3d 298, 574 N.E.2d 522. On motion for rehearing. Rehearing denied.

Douglas and Resnick, JJ., dissent. Wright, J., not participating. Moyer, C.J., and H. Brown, J., would also grant the motion to strike. Wright, J., not participating.
